{"tid":2068564,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港台 視點31","createTime":"2020-06-17T19:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T19:49:08.000Z","uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b130b18ce6789ab012f93f3f0a7cffb0725ae741","tid":2068564,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:07:56.000Z","msg":"呢單好明顯係完勝黎，咪撚再話我地呢邊嘈交一定輸<br />\n作為一個中學校長，鄧飛同一個大學生辯論，本身係資歷上已經唔對等，居然都要用到泥漿摔角，老屈觀點打稻草人，莫須有呢d招式黎狡辯。佢提出嘅所有觀點，鄭同學都有明確作出辯駁，跟住還擊唔到唯有不停以點解要係學校搞港獨扯開話題，儘管已多次話否認冇搞過港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">你討論還討論，結論必須只得一個</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後鄧飛話你可以send意見去特首辦，鄭同學回左句send意見有效改變到政府就唔使200萬人上街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然貴為中學校長，竟然都冇能力用論點去駁贏人，真心為呢個政權嘅教育制度感到悲哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SfquAI7mNdc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSfquAI7mNdc&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=c19a2299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SfquAI7mNdc</a>"},{"pid":"4c3e6f51f62963090bab8b15e235f406c984f2cf","tid":2068564,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}